oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Eddy Arnold - RCA Studio Recordings
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Eddy Arnold (musician) studio background tracks. The recordings were created for RCA Records. The recordings take place on a variety unidentified dates.
